#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repetitive Strain Injury can occur as a result of working with a mouse and "
"keyboard. This utility can be used to remind you to take a break now and "
"then. It displays a random picture from a collection at specified intervals "
"for defined durations. You can configure the pictures to show and lengths of "
"time to show them. You might use the breaks reminders to do some stretching "
"exercises, for example, or as a reminder to walk away from the computer for "
"a while."
msgstr ""
"Poškodba zaradi ponavljajočih se gibov se lahko pojavi kot posledica dela z "
"miško in tipkovnico. Ta pripomoček lahko uporabite, da vas opomni, da si "
"občasno vzamete odmor. Prikaže naključno sliko iz zbirke v določenih "
"intervalih za določena obdobja. Konfigurirate lahko slike za prikaz in čas "
"njihovega prikaza. Opomnike za odmore lahko uporabite, na primer, da "
"naredite nekaj razteznih vaj ali kot opomnik, da za nekaj časa odidete stran "
"od računalnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Logo &rsibreak;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Logo &rsibreak;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Logo &rsibreak;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Logo &rsibreak;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rsibreak; was originally written by Tom Albers. Early in the development "
"Bram Schoenmakers joined the project"
msgstr ""
"&rsibreak; je prvotno napisal Tom Albers. Na začetku razvoja se je projektu "
"pridružil Bram Schoenmakers"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &rsibreak;"
msgstr "Uporaba &rsibreak;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea of &rsibreak; is to interrupt you in your work. The intention is to "
"do that in a user-friendly manner. There will be times, though, that it will "
"display itself when you are very busy. The configuration options in "
"&rsibreak; are an effort to allow you to customize the interruptions. In "
"that way we hope you will be able to improve your effectiveness at work "
"while lessening your chances of injury."
msgstr ""
"Zamisel &rsibreak; je, da vas zmoti pri vašem delu. Namen je to narediti na "
"uporabniku prijazen način. Vendar se bo včasih prikazalo samo, ko boste zelo "
"zaposleni. Konfiguracijske možnosti v &rsibreak; si prizadevajo, da bi vam "
"omogočili prilagajanje prekinitev. Upamo, da boste na ta način lahko "
"izboljšali svojo učinkovitost pri delu in hkrati zmanjšali možnosti za "
"poškodbe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After starting, you can see an icon in your tray and you will see a welcome "
"pop up. Although the application should be useful with default settings, it "
"may be wise to take control by examining the settings. To discover and to "
"obtain an access to the options available, right click on the tray icon; in "
"the context menu that appears, select <guilabel>Configure</guilabel>. The "
"following chapters contain further configuration information."
msgstr ""
"Po zagonu lahko vidite ikono v pladnju in videli boste pozdravno pojavno "
"okno. Čeprav bi morala biti aplikacija uporabna s privzetimi nastavitvami, "
"je morda pametno prevzeti nadzor tako, da pregledate nastavitve. Če želite "
"odkriti in pridobiti dostop do razpoložljivih možnosti, z desno miškino "
"tipko kliknite ikono v pladnju; v kontekstnem meniju, ki se prikaže, "
"izberite <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>. Naslednja poglavja vsebujejo "
"dodatne informacije o konfiguraciji."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "&rsibreak; statistics"
msgstr "&rsibreak; statistika"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left click on the tray icon to see statistics"
msgstr "Levi klik na ikono pladnja za ogled statistike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you left click on the tray icon you will see some statistics. If you "
"configure &rsibreak; to break at fixed times your idle time will not be "
"measured. In that case, some of the options in the statistics may not be "
"very informative."
msgstr ""
"Ko z levim gumbom kliknete ikono pladnja, boste videli nekaj statističnih "
"podatkov. Če konfigurirate &rsibreak; za prekinitev ob določenih urah vaš "
"čas nedejavnosti ne bo izmerjen. V tem primeru nekatere možnosti v "
"statistiki morda niso preveč informativne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The upper left block shows general statistics: some totals and some "
"information about idle time. The bottom left block shows something about "
"your work pace. You will see the total amount of activity since you started "
"the current log-in session. The amount of activity during some other "
"intervals will also be shown. The Pause Score decreases every time you skip "
"a break. The blocks to the right report on which short and long breaks have "
"already passed. At present, the labels in the dialog can either be black or "
"red and green. In the latter case a red statistic indicates a recommendation "
"to relax and take a break, which will bring the color closer to green."
msgstr ""
"Zgornji levi blok prikazuje splošno statistiko: nekaj skupnih vrednosti in "
"nekaj informacij o času nedejavnosti. Spodnji levi blok prikazuje nekaj o "
"vašem delovnem tempu. Videli boste skupno količino dejavnosti od začetka "
"trenutne seje prijave. Prikazana bo tudi količina aktivnosti v nekaterih "
"drugih intervalih. Ocena premora se zmanjša vsakič, ko preskočite odmor. "
"Bloki na desni poročajo, kateri kratki in dolgi odmori so že minili. "
"Trenutno so oznake v pogovornem oknu lahko črne ali rdeče in zelene. V "
"slednjem primeru rdeča statistika označuje priporočilo za sprostitev in "
"odmor, kar bo barvo približalo zeleni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you right-click the tray icon, the context menu will show an option to "
"<guilabel>Suspend</guilabel> &rsibreak;. When you don't want to be "
"interrupted, such as during a game or a presentation, you can use this to "
"silence &rsibreak; You can resume &rsibreak; when you click right on the "
"icon again and select <guilabel>Resume</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ko z desno miškino tipko kliknete ikono pladnja, se v kontekstnem meniju "
"prikaže možnost <guilabel>Začasno ustavi</guilabel> &rsibreak;. Ko ne "
"želite, da vas motijo, na primer med igro ali predstavitvijo, lahko to "
"uporabite za utišanje &rsibreak; Lahko nadaljujete &rsibreak; ko znova "
"kliknete desno na ikono in izberete <guilabel>Nadaljuj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suspended &rsibreak;"
msgstr "Odloženo &rsibreak;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tray icon when &rsibreak; is suspended"
msgstr "Ikona pladnja, ko &rsibreak; je odložen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last way to influence &rsibreak; is via &DBus;. There are &DBus; "
"commands available to force breaks and to suspend and resume &rsibreak;. You "
"can use these to suspend &rsibreak; automatically when you start a game or "
"any other specified program. Execute <command>qdbus org.kde.rsibreak /"
"rsibreak</command> to see the possibilities."
msgstr ""
"Zadnji način vplivanja na &rsibreak; je prek &DBus;. Obstaja &DBus; ukaz, ki "
"so na voljo za prisilne prekinitve ter za prekinitev in nadaljevanje "
"&rsibreak;. Te lahko uporabite za zaustavitev &rsibreak; samodejno, ko "
"zaženete igro ali kateri koli drug določen program. Izvedite <command>qdbus "
"org.kde.rsibreak /rsibreak</command>, da si ogledate možnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Break types"
msgstr "Vrste odmorov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most settings are straightforward. On the general page, there is an option "
"to start up automatically at &kde; startup. You might wonder why that is "
"because the session manager should take care of that. Some users may need to "
"start &rsibreak; at startup while they are not using the session manager. "
"Note that <application>Gnome</application> will ignore the setting."
msgstr ""
"Večina nastavitev je enostavnih. Na splošni strani obstaja možnost "
"samodejnega zagona ob zagonu &kde;. Morda se sprašujete, zakaj je tako, ker "
"bi moral za to poskrbeti upravitelj seje. Nekateri uporabniki bodo morda "
"morali zagnati &rsibreak; ob zagonu, ko ne uporabljajo upravitelja sej. "
"Upoštevajte, da bo <application>Gnome</application> prezrl nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two behavior options in &rsibreak;. There is an option to break at "
"fixed intervals for fixed periods, and there is an option to reset the "
"timers when &rsibreak; detects that you have been idle for the duration of a "
"break."
msgstr ""
"V &rsibreak; sta na voljo dve možnosti obnašanja. Obstaja možnost prekinitve "
"v določenih intervalih za določena obdobja in možnost ponastavitve "
"časovnikov, ko &rsibreak; zazna, da ste med odmorom mirovali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can indicate that you do not want RSIBreak to interfere with "
"presentations, games, video playback, and any other fullscreen application "
"on the current virtual desktop using the <guilabel>Suppress if fullscreen "
"windows present</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Lahko označite, da ne želite, da RSIBreak moti predstavitve, igre, "
"predvajanje videa in katero koli drugo celozaslonsko aplikacijo na trenutnem "
"navideznem namizju z možnostjo <guilabel>Zavrni, če so prisotna "
"celozaslonska okna</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "&rsibreak; popup"
msgstr "&rsibreak; pojavno okno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lock button enables you to lock your screen whenever you leave your "
"computer"
msgstr ""
"Gumb za zaklepanje vam omogoča, da zaklenete zaslon, kadar koli zapustite "
"računalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may find the full-screen notice to take a break inconvenient at the time "
"it appears. In this case, on the <guilabel>During Breaks</guilabel> page you "
"can indicate that you want to use a popup; a small popup near the tray will "
"appear asking you to take a break. If you choose to ignore that, the full-"
"screen activity-block will appear anyway."
msgstr ""
"Morda se vam zdi celozaslonsko obvestilo o prekinitvi neprijetno, ko se "
"prikaže. V tem primeru lahko na strani <guilabel>Med prekinitvami</guilabel> "
"označite, da želite uporabiti pojavno okno; v bližini pladnja se prikaže "
"majhno pojavno okno, ki vas poziva, da si vzamete odmor. Če se odločite, da "
"to prezrete, se bo vseeno prikazal celozaslonski blok dejavnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are three options for the full screen break. It can show a "
"<guilabel>Complete Black Effect</guilabel> (this is the default action), "
"<guilabel>Show Plasma Dashboard</guilabel> or <guilabel>Show Slide Show of "
"Images</guilabel> where a path may be set up to specify a folder on your "
"hard disk which contains images. During a break, you will see a slideshow of "
"those images."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo tri možnosti za celozaslonsko prekinitev. Lahko prikaže "
"<guilabel>Popoln črni učinek</guilabel> (to je privzeto dejanje), "
"<guilabel>Pokaže nadzorno ploščo Plasma</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Pokaži "
"predstavitev slik</guilabel>, kjer je lahko pot nastavite tako, da določite "
"mapo na trdem disku, ki vsebuje slike. Med odmorom boste videli predstavitev "
"teh slik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duration/Interval of a break"
msgstr "Trajanje/interval prekinitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rsibreak; supports two different types of break: <quote>Tiny breaks</quote> "
"and <quote>Big breaks</quote>. The usual way to use these is to take "
"frequent tiny breaks, and occasional big breaks. For example, a break of 20 "
"seconds every 20 minutes (the tiny break), and a longer break of 2 minutes "
"every hour (the big break)."
msgstr ""
"&rsibreak; podpira dve različni vrsti prekinitev: <quote>Drobne odmore</"
"quote> in <quote>Velike odmore</quote>. Običajni način uporabe teh je "
"pogosti majhni odmori in občasni veliki odmori. Na primer, 20-sekundni odmor "
"vsakih 20 minut (majhen odmor) in daljši 2-minutni odmor vsako uro (veliki "
"odmor)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is no use to set up intervals which are irritating. Those will, by "
"definition, get on your nerves and you will be more likely to hit &Esc; "
"&ndash; or any other key you have setup on the <guilabel>During Breaks</"
"guilabel> page &ndash; to skip the break."
msgstr ""
"Nima smisla postavljati intervalov, ki so dražljivi. Ti vam bodo po "
"definiciji šli na živce in bolj verjetno boste zadeli &Esc; &ndash; ali "
"katero koli drugo tipko, ki ste jo nastavili na strani <guilabel>Med odmori</"
"guilabel> &ndash; kako preskočiti odmor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find that you are often skipping breaks, you could decide to disable "
"the shortcut and hide the minimize button. Remember, you choose how strictly "
"to follow the break sequence."
msgstr ""
"Če ugotovite, da pogosto preskakujete odmore, se lahko odločite, da "
"onemogočite bližnjico in skrijete gumb za pomanjšanje. Ne pozabite, da sami "
"izberete, kako natančno boste sledili zaporedju prekinitev."

